highlights.text: Sid Sriram has the most spots on Top Songs Hyderabad. “Urike Urike” is the highest at #7.
“Emo Emo - From "Raahu"” by Praveen Lakkaraju and Sid Sriram has been on Top Songs Hyderabad the longest, at 61 weeks straight.
“Thenmozhi (From "Thiruchitrambalam")” by Santhosh Narayanan and Anirudh Ravichander is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hyderabad, up 15 spots at #40.
“Almost Padipoyindhe Pilla (From "Das Ka Dhamki")” by Leon James, Adithya RK, and Poornachari is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hyderabad at #6.
